<subSubSection id="CEBA6578FFE2ED5DCEECF894FE78BB93" pageId="7" pageNumber="443" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="861F36F3FFE2ED5DCEECF894FE78BB93" blockId="7.[151,1436,866,1971]" pageId="7" pageNumber="443">
<emphasis id="B4D4EAE1FFE2ED5DCEECF894FEFEBB03" bold="true" box="[199,335,1802,1827]" pageId="7" pageNumber="443">Comments.</emphasis>
The identity of this species remains unclear. Two species are known from adjacent parts of India, 
<taxonomicName id="41A04D70FFE2ED5DCEBCF8B1FEC7BB67" authority="Smith" authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1879" box="[151,374,1838,1863]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Anthidium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="443" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ordinatum">
<emphasis id="B4D4EAE1FFE2ED5DCEBCF8B1FE98BB67" box="[151,297,1838,1863]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="443">A. ordinatum</emphasis>
Smith
</taxonomicName>
, type locality “Bombay Presidency” and 
<taxonomicName id="41A04D70FFE2ED5DCD6BF8B1FB3FBB67" authority="Mavromoustakis" authorityName="Mavromoustakis" authorityYear="1948" box="[832,1166,1838,1863]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Anthidium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="443" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longstaffi">
<emphasis id="B4D4EAE1FFE2ED5DCD6BF8B1FC79BB67" box="[832,968,1838,1863]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="443">A. longstaffi</emphasis>
Mavromoustakis
</taxonomicName>
, type locality Matheran, Maharashtra. The present material does not appear to match descriptions of either and may represent an undescribed species, but without additional material and study of the types of 
<taxonomicName id="41A04D70FFE2ED5DCA30F8E9FB01BBAF" authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1879" box="[1051,1200,1910,1935]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Anthidium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="443" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ordinatum">
<emphasis id="B4D4EAE1FFE2ED5DCA30F8E9FB01BBAF" box="[1051,1200,1910,1935]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="443">A. ordinatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="41A04D70FFE2ED5DCAC7F8E9FAC6BBAF" authorityName="Mavromoustakis" authorityYear="1948" box="[1260,1399,1910,1935]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Anthidium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="443" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="longstaffi">
<emphasis id="B4D4EAE1FFE2ED5DCAC7F8E9FAC6BBAF" box="[1260,1399,1910,1935]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="443">A. longstaffi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
no such decision can be made.
</paragraph>
